<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَلَا لِبَنِي هَاشِمٍ، وَهُمْ سُلَالَتُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَلَا مَوَالِيهِمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَإِنْ دَفَعَهَا لِغَيْرِ مُسْتَحِقِّهَا لِجَهْلٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> ثُمَّ عَلِمَ حَالَهُ:</span> لَمْ تُجْزِئْهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- إِلَّا لِغَنِيٍّ ظَنَّهُ فَقِيرًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَتُسَنُّ صَدَقَةُ التَّطَوُّعِ كُلَّ وَقْتٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَكَوْنُهَا:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> سِرًّا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> بِطِيبِ نَفْسٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> فِي صِحَّةٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَرَمَضَانَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥]</span> وَوَقْتِ حَاجَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٦]</span> <span style="color:#707070">[٧]</span> وَفِي كُلِّ زَمَانٍ، وَمَكَانٍ فَاضِلٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٨]</span> وَعَلَى جَارٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٩]</span> وَذَوِي رَحِمٍ لَا سِيَّمَا مَعَ عَدَاوَةٍ، -وَهِيَ صَدَقَةٌ وَصِلَةٌ-.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أَفْضَلُ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>- وَالمَنُّ بِالصَّدَقَةِ كَبِيرَةٌ، وَيَبْطُلُ الثَّوابُ بِهِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>